content:
Form Format in Secure Forms Is Generally Available in Messaging for In-App and Web.

Previously, the Form format was in beta for Messaging for In-App and Web. The change now makes it generally available, similar to its status in enhanced Apple Messages for Business channels.

Where: This applies to Messaging for In-App and Web. View required editions.

SEE ALSO
Create and Send Secure Forms in Messaging Sessions (can be outdated or unavailable during release preview)
title: Form Format Availability in Secure Forms
